client downloads: [url=http://uppit.com/v/ER18MS48]http://uppit.com/v/ER18MS48[/url] [url=http://www.multiupload.com/WFC7JN2H0J]http://www.multiupload.com/WFC7JN2H0J[/url] Source link : http://uppit.com/v/PSCJHMSM upgraded link: http://uppit.com/v/1XH9T745 Features
[ul][*]- Our pk point protection is unbreakable. New accounts cannot attack for 30 minutes. You cannot receive points from killing the same player within your last 5 kills.
[*]- An area dedicated to skilling.
[*]- Zamorak godwars. Get 20 kills and pray at the altar to be teleported to K'ril.
[*]- More options for pest control rewards.
[*]- No custom items. The only items in the server are items that are actually in Runescape.
[*]- A custom pk point exchange. This will even allow you to receive and weild a firecape without defeating Jad.
[*]- Uses array lists for a random choice of items for pk rewards.
[*]- An experience rate of 800xp per hit. Magic has an experience rate that is roughly the same speed.
[*]- Must use client only.
[*]- Great staff.
[*]- Has anti x-logs to prevent people xlogging in your fights.
[*]- Has a Tramp at home to reset your skills if you wish.
[*]- Has Rabbit hop emote, who wouldn't enjoy this???
[*]- Has exp lock via quest tab.
[*]- Many enjoyable mini games.
[*]- Lots of shops.
[*]- Home is located in Edgevill.
[*]- Big training area with good drops.
[*]- Lunar magic book is changeable.
[*]- Not too easy to level up, so you won't get bored right when you get there.
[*]- Different types of monsters in the monsters teleport.
[*]- Many different places to go.[/ul]
